{
  "stem": "25348.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We grabbed a couple of ill-fitting garments, my mother and I, and we left.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "However, before I tell you-- I continue with this, I want to tell you about the incidents.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I just told you about the Poles who looked at Jewish clothing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I saw these men, these bearded Jews, who were pushed to the pit.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Neat German precision, they had to put their clothing on the ground, but they never parted with their skull caps.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "When they fell, this was in my mind.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They held onto their caps, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] and [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they chanted.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I couldn't understand the chants.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But it was a kind of an act of defiance.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Neither did the German know what they were chanting.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They were talking to God.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "That's what I wanted-- that's an unforgettable moment.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Now I shall tell you, getting out of hell, we didn't know which direction to take.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we walked for about two days.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] Then we were hiding.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We came across a stretch of a field [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] which was half harvested, and it had stalks of beans.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we were hiding in this-- behind those beans for a few days.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But when we got up one morning, we could see the ground sort of getting balder.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They were harvesting on the other side of the field.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And they would probably get closer to us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Not talking about diarrhea or-- because we ate just the leaves from the beans.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We had nothing else.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So Mother and I reached the main road.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And suddenly, a, a milk delivery truck stopped.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
